#: ../../postinstall.rst:54
msgid ""
"**1. Boot Multi User:** This is the default option for booting |trueos|. The"
" system automatically uses this option either after pausing for a few "
"moments or if :kbd:`Enter` is pressed while the boot menu is displayed."
