#: ../../postinstall.rst:104
msgid ""
"**4. Safe Mode:** Select this option if the installation hangs when probing "
"hardware and :guilabel:`3 ACPI Support` did not help. It will boot with a "
"forced PIO mode (disabling the use of DMA), disable write caching for all "
"IDE hard drives and CD-ROM drives, and disable the probing of EISA slots (as"
" very few systems have them)."
msgstr ""

